{"tid":2432842,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"確診翁播毒美心等至少2藍店　嘉里控股秘書染疫食藍店simplylife","createTime":"2021-03-04T14:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T15:01:23.000Z","uid":261647,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c9755ef5c8ba6c8ce35a50f1650c6a239913cde2","tid":2432842,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/24SJCFTR6ZA5PHNTLWDPPEOBNE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2F24SJCFTR6ZA5PHNTLWDPPEOBNE%2F&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=3212d2fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2F24SJCFTR6ZA5PHNTLWDPPEOBNE%2F&h=c6d52f7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/24SJCFTR6ZA5PHNTLWDPPEOBNE/</a><br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心披露，周三（3日）新增的其中2宗源頭不明確診，傳染期（發病前2日起計）行蹤頗多。其中住柴灣的69歲退休男，除傳染期去過美心MX和麗香園冰室2間藍店，由發病當日至3日後，更去過4間餐廳。至於住康城的53歲嘉里控股女秘書，除傳染期去過藍店美心旗下的simplylife，又帶病前往曾奪米芝蓮一星的南海一號，發病後8日仍到鰂魚涌嘉里中心上班。嘉里控股所有同事都要強制檢測。"},{"pid":"41d5773b6ca392b3e27be4e7d9f03599fb07c8f7","tid":2432842,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9755ef5c8ba6c8ce35a50f1650c6a239913cde2","tid":2432842,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/24SJCFTR6ZA5PHNTLWDPPEOBNE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2F24SJCFTR6ZA5PHNTLWDPPEOBNE%2F&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=3212d2fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2F24SJCFTR6ZA5PHNTLWDPPEOBNE%2F&h=c6d52f7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/24SJCFTR6ZA5PHNTLWDPPEOBNE/</a><br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心披露，周三（3日）新增的其中2宗源頭不明確診，傳染期（發病前2日起計）行蹤頗多。其中住柴灣的69歲退休男，除傳染期去過美心MX和麗香園冰室2間藍店，由發病當日至3日後，更去過4間餐廳。至於住康城的53歲嘉里控股女秘